title: The New Tsars 04 - Revolution, Revolution (2007, Delitte) (2016,
description:
Series conclusion !
In the middle of an oil crisis, corruption, and Islamic revolution, the Russian mafia reigns supreme.

Masterfully manoeuvred by Gunter, a German mercenary in the service of powerful Arab emirates, rebels stalk the oligarchs in suburban Baku. After the murder of his friend, Yuri joins the rebel leader while the president, determined to escape, is forced to unleash a reluctant army.
The revolutionaries don't suspect they are being controlled by powers beyond their noble intentions... as Yuri again discovers that it's not always wise to speak the truth...

enjoy
